int:&#10;191;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/anti-fraud/sites/default/files/c_2021_5338_f1_annex_en.pdf   \" target=\"_blank\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">EUAF&nbsp;</span><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><span style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">Work Programme 2021</span></span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><a href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/ALL/?uri=CELEX:32021R0785\" target=\"_blank\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">EUAF</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; line-height: 15.3333px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">&nbsp;Regulation 2021/785</span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\"><br />\r\n</span><a href=\"https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/ALL/?uri=CELEX:32018R1046&amp;qid=1535046024012\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">EU Financial Regulation 2018/1046</span></a></p>", "supportInfo": "<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">For help related to this</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">&nbsp;</span><b style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">call</b><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">, please contact:</span><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal;\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/support/faq;grantAndTendertype=1;categories=p_submission_eval;programme=null;actions=;keyword=;period=null\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Funding &amp; Tenders Portal FAQ</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&ndash; Submission of proposals.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal;\"><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/portal/screen/support/helpdesks/contact-form\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">IT Helpdesk</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&ndash; Contact the IT helpdesk for questions such as forgotten passwords, access rights and roles, technical aspects of submission of proposals, etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal;\"><a href=\"https://webgate.ec.europa.eu/funding-tenders-opportunities/display/OM/Online+Manual\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Online Manual</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&ndash; Step-by-step online guide through the Portal processes from proposal preparation and submission to reporting on your on-going project. Valid for all 2021-2027 programmes.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal;\">For non-IT related questions, please contact the functional mailboxes mentioned in section 12 of the <a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/info/funding-tenders/opportunities/docs/2021-2027/euaf/wp-call/2021/call-fiche_euaf-2021-ta_euaf-2021-trai_en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">call document</a></p>", "sepTemplate": "<p>To access the Electronic Submission Service, please click on the submission-button next to the <strong>type of action</strong> and the <strong>type of model grant agreement</strong> that corresponds to your proposal. You will then be asked to confirm your choice, as it cannot be changed in the submission system. Upon confirmation, you will be linked to the correct entry point.</p>\r\n<p>To access existing draft proposals for this topic, please login to the Funding &amp; Tenders Portal and select the My Proposals page of the My Area section.</p>", "links": [], "additionalDossiers": [], "infoPackDossiers": [], "callDetailsJSONItem": {"staticAdditionalInfo": "<p><span><span>Union Anti-Fraud Programme (UAFP) </span></span><span><span>funded actions aim <strong>to protect the financial interests of the European Union <u>by preventing and combating</u> </strong>fraud, corruption and any other illegal activities affecting the financial interests of the Union.</span></span></p><p>Among others, the programme encourages the reinforcement of investigative capability and capacity of national authorities, including their digitalisation, in view of stepping up the fight against fraud, corruption and any other illegal activity affecting the financial interests of the European Union, on both the revenue and expenditure sides.</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span><span>Maximum project duration</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span><span>: </span></span></span><span><span>Project duration should normally range between 12 and 24 months</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span><span>The indicative available budget for grants for this Call is </span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color:#00B050;\"><span><span>EUR 9 300 000</span></span></span></strong><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span><span>.</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span><span>The grants will cover a maximum of <strong>80%</strong> (<strong>90% in exceptional </strong>and duly justified cases ) of the eligible costs of the action.</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span><span>The minimum threshold for the TOTAL budgeted costs of a project submitted is set at <strong>EUR 100 000</strong>. Therefore, the REQUESTED GRANT for the action must be at least <strong>EUR 80 000</strong> (80% of EUR 100 000).</span></span></span></p>\n", "latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "Jul 22, 2021 12:00:00 AM", "lastChangeDate": "Jul 22, 2021 12:00:00 AM", "content": "The submission session is now available for: EUAF-2021-TA-04(EUAF-PJG), EUAF-2021-TA-03(EUAF-PJG), EUAF-2021-TA-01(EUAF-PJG), EUAF-2021-TA-02(EUAF-PJG)"}], "hasForthcomingTopics": false, "hasOpenTopics": false, "allClosedTopics": true}}}